# This branch (`release`) is the public showroom for github.com/Hilopio/PRIMO.
# It must contain ONLY documentation and one small sample dataset. Everything
# else is ignored so that a plain `git add .` can never leak source code, the
# wheel, or dev leftovers into the showroom repo. Development happens on other
# branches, where these files are tracked and therefore unaffected by this list.
/*
!.gitignore
!LICENSE
!NOTICE
!README.md
!THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md

# Ship one lightweight example (~9 MB) so users can try `primo-stitch` at once.
!examples/
examples/*
!examples/metal_series/
